title: Journey Home
description: I loved listening to this CD in the early 90s, went looking for it the other day and couldn't find it. Sadly, it's stuck at 99.7% on Pirate Bay and, it looks like, everywhere else. So, unable to find it complete, I used Soundflower to copy from an Internet streaming service into Audacity and encode the music into 320kbps mp3 audio. I hope you enjoy it...PLEASE SEED!
